@@TJvCreateShortcut
Description:
This component let you Create shortcut on the desktop/startup menu/everywhere...

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCreateShortcut.CreateDesktopShortcut@string@string@string
Description:
This method will Create a shortcut on the desktop

Parameters:
FileName: 
is the path to the FileName
Parameters: 
is the param you want to pass to the executable
Linkname: 
is the name you want to see in the start menu

Returns:
The path of the shortcut created

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCreateShortcut.CreateShortcut@string@string@string@string
Description:
This method will Create a shortcut in a directory

Parameters:
FileName: 
is the path to the FileName
Parameters: 
is the param you want to pass to the executable
linkname: 
is the name you want to see in the start menu
Directory: 
is the directory in which you want to see the shortcut

Returns:
the path of the shortcut created

